<fig>
<cap>A&mdash;MORTAR. B&mdash;OPEN END OF MORTAR. C&mdash;SLAB OF ROCK. D&mdash;IRON SOLE PLATES.
E&mdash;SCREEN. F&mdash;LAUNDER. G&mdash;WOODEN SHOVEL. H&mdash;SETTLING PIT. I&mdash;IRON
